	10 data 0, 18.110963, 18.183994, 18.470829, 18.596143, 18.728113, 18.783888, 18.939737, 19.309439, 19.452922, 19.511199, 19.601024, 19.678168, 19.685513, 19.705497, 19.722377, 19.751315, 19.761010, 19.799188, 19.808400,
