	10 data 0, 16.810000, 16.930000, 17.490000, 17.960000, 18.929766, 19.102849, 19.167658, 19.277741, 19.372807, 19.378359, 19.401620, 19.424639, 19.459149, 19.473101, 19.521369, 19.537205,
